&lt;p&gt;
	Install Instructions:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Copy the contents of the zip to your plugin directory, change the default language constant in i18n_base.php, and replace the following functions in your template(s) with their I18N variants:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	get_component with get_i18n_component&lt;br /&gt;
	get_navigation with get_i18n_navigation&lt;/p&gt;
